# CapturedRoom.ModelProvider.Error.attributeCombinationNotSupported

**Case**

An error that indicates the framework doesn’t support the attributes set in a model-URL query.

## Declaration

```swift
case attributeCombinationNotSupported
```

## Discussion

This error occurs for the [doc://com.apple.RoomPlan/documentation/RoomPlan/CapturedRoom/ModelProvider/modelFileURL(for:)-58ykp] function when an unsupported combination of attributes resides in the argument array.

## Interpreting the error

- **CapturedRoom.ModelProvider.Error.nonExistingFile(url:)**: An error that indicates a model-URL query failed to return a result.
